  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game is Now Available for Early Access!</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 chapters of linear main storyline, with 30 main levels<br></li><li>10 different playable characters<br></li><li>A talent tree system with 26 unique large talent points<br></li><li>A chip system with over 100 attribute-enhancing entries<br></li><li>30 additional challenging free-play levels</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2></strong><br>Mystery of Dust is an <strong>RPG game</strong> with <strong>tower defense strategy elements</strong>. Players take on the role of \"Lisha Komo,\" a girl caught in an \"intelligent machine rebellion\" sweeping the city. Granted the powerful \"Memory Core,\" she uses \"Heroic Memories\" from past wars to fight. Due to her unique abilities, she forms a team to resolve the rebellion and uncover its source.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D Tower Defense Battles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/5e5b389deb5b611b26bb274eef6d4de9.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/5e5b389deb5b611b26bb274eef6d4de9.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/5e5b389deb5b611b26bb274eef6d4de9.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Deserts, factories, nights, days... Use your Memory Core to strategize and defeat various enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Memory Cores</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/dce386286674a1d0945307532e51217a.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/dce386286674a1d0945307532e51217a.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/dce386286674a1d0945307532e51217a.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>10 playable Memory Cores, each with a unique skill. Understand their uses and form a cohesive team!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chip Equipment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/fd137cc46dc59b42bd2c41a447f3d104.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/fd137cc46dc59b42bd2c41a447f3d104.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/fd137cc46dc59b42bd2c41a447f3d104.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A chip system with over 100 attribute-enhancing entries. Unique set chip effects can drastically change combat styles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Talent System</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/7adb1b7ed1a5914b65be226e13efd072.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/7adb1b7ed1a5914b65be226e13efd072.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/7adb1b7ed1a5914b65be226e13efd072.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A large talent tree to customize your team's strengths and weaknesses, supporting your strategy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Levels</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/32dfdc57111906cbe2d0cb9c195cfe5b.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/32dfdc57111906cbe2d0cb9c195cfe5b.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/32dfdc57111906cbe2d0cb9c195cfe5b.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Free-play levels graded by difficulty, offering additional rewards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Linear Storyline</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/3052d4e01e43886aaab9bbb741149d68.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/3052d4e01e43886aaab9bbb741149d68.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/3052d4e01e43886aaab9bbb741149d68.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Follow Lisha's journey through a captivating storyline.",
